# Jun Hao Skill-Based Gentleman Agent — v4

## What changed from v3

| # | Optimization | Detail |
|---|-------------|--------|
| 1 | **Parallel skills** | `reflect` + `analyze` run concurrently via `ThreadPoolExecutor`. ~45% latency reduction per reply. |
| 2 | **Incremental memory compression** | Only compresses new messages since last snapshot, then merges with existing snapshot. No information loss on repeat compressions. |
| 3 | **Auto-think behavior memory** | Tracks last spontaneous message time + whether user responded. Backs off if ignored. |
| 4 | **Context role separation** | `reflection` and `analysis` passed via `system` role, not stuffed into `user` message. Model correctly interprets internal vs external voices. |
| 5 | **Retry decorator** | All LLM calls retry up to 2 times on empty/null response. Silent failures eliminated. |
| 6 | **Personality anchor** | `CORE_IDENTITY` re-injected as a system reminder before history on every compose call. History cannot overwrite identity. |

---

## Architecture

```
User input
    │
    ├─ Hard block? ──────────────────────────────► Refuse + stop
    ├─ High risk? ───────────────────────────────► Direct compose (no routing)
    │
    ▼
skill_route()  ← temperature 0.0, deterministic
    │
    ├── FACTUAL ──► skill_search() (web)
    │                    │
    │    ┌───────────────┘
    │    │
    ▼    ▼  [PARALLEL]
skill_reflect()   skill_analyze()
    │                   │
    └────────┬──────────┘
             │
             ▼
       skill_compose()
       [system: identity anchor + reflection + analysis]
       [history: trimmed recent]
       [user: original input only]
             │
             ▼
       skill_output()  ← sentence-by-sentence
             │
             ▼
       _maybe_compress()  ← incremental if threshold hit
```

---

## Quick Reference

| Config | Default | Effect |
|--------|---------|--------|
| `MODEL_NAME` | `"gpt-4o-mini"` | Any LiteLLM model string |
| `TEMPERATURE` | `0.72` | Response creativity |
| `COMPRESS_THRESHOLD` | `60` | New messages since last snapshot before re-compress |
| `COMPRESS_KEEP_RECENT` | `10` | Raw messages kept after compression |
| `AUTO_THINK_INTERVAL` | `120` | Seconds of silence before autonomous message |
| `AUTO_THINK_BACKOFF` | `3` | Max ignored spontaneous messages before agent goes quiet |
| `MAX_RETRY` | `2` | LLM call retry attempts on empty response |

