## Extending Skills

```python
# 1. 定义新 skill 方法
def skill_cultural_context(self, user_input: str) -> str:
    return with_retry(lambda: self._call(
        [{"role": "system", "content": self._system() + "\nFocus on cultural subtext."},
         {"role": "user", "content": user_input}],
        temperature=0.7, max_tokens=200
    ))()

# 2. 加入并发块
f_culture = ex.submit(self.skill_cultural_context, user_input)
culture   = f_culture.result()

# 3. 传入 compose（更新签名）
reply_text = self.skill_compose(user_input, reflection, analysis, facts, culture)
```

