## Common Issues

| Problem | Cause | Fix |
|---------|-------|-----|
| `AuthenticationError` | Missing API key | `export OPENAI_API_KEY=...` |
| `Model not found` | Wrong model string | Check LiteLLM model list |
| Auto-think output mixed with prompt | Terminal `input()` limitation | 正常现象，按 Enter 刷新显示 |
| Memory never compresses | 消息数不够 | 测试时把 `COMPRESS_THRESHOLD` 改成 10 |
| Parallel hits rate limit | 并发请求过多 | 把 `max_workers` 改成 2 |
| JSON parse error in compress | 模型加了 markdown fence | 已被 `strip_fences()` 处理，若仍报错检查模型输出 |
